1. I want to keep all filters, i dont want to add a new one.
Use simple agg. functions such as SUM(), MIN(), MAX()

2. I want to keep all filters and add a new filter.
Use a combination of CALCULATE(), FILTER()

3. I want to remove one or more filters and I do not
want to add a new ones.
Use a combination of CALCULATE(), ALL()

4. I want to change an existing filter, 
Use a combination of CALCULATE() and a condition
for example year = 2022
